results.title: Tea light candle tray, 3 tea light candle holder, live laugh love glass candle tray, pink glass jewelry holder, rectangle 3 well ring tray.
results.description:
Tea light candle tray, 3 tea light candle holder, pink glass glass jewelry tray, pink swirl "live, laugh, love" glass jewelry holder, rectangle tray for jewelry storage.

This tray is so unique with 3 individual wells for tea light or jewelry or just about anything your imagination has for it.  This tray is slim and long to let it fit in may different areas of the house.  The glass is a unique pink swirl, with many different shades of pink.  At the bottom of each well is a porcelain decal of the popular saying of "live laugh love" in thick black script.   The decal saying are special decals that are made for glass and are fired on by the kiln to keep them permanent and stand up to gentle washing.  The combination of the beautiful pink swirl glass and the wonderful inspirational saying and the unique shape this tray is a must have.  The tray is separated into 3 separate compartments that is perfect fit for a tea light or a smaller decorative candle.  Each compartment is raised to make little squares.  These square compartments can be filled with small stones or shell's for the tea light candle also.  This little tray is not limited to tea light candles, it is great for holding jewelry, small office supplies, or even spoons as a spoon rest.  The uses for this little tray is only limited by your imagination and the inspirational saying will give your mood a boost at the same time.

This tray is made from 2 pieces of glass that is fused together in a kiln, then it is placed in a mold to make the dished tray form.  Each compartment is a square with raised edges, the squares are about 3" each.  Each compartment has a different saying. This is a one of a kind item.

This is designed and made by me in my smoke free home studio.  Measurement's may vary slightly due to the organic nature of the glass and that it is hand measured, but I try to be as accurate as possible.

Any questions please feel free to ask.  The glass is food safe.  Do not place in the microwave, oven or dishwasher.  Please hand wash only.
